  "description": "Fix Gallery Filter Button Layout and Display\n\nResolve layout issues causing gallery filter buttons to render incorrectly or be cut off from view.\n\nRequirements:\n- Identify and fix CSS/styling issues preventing all filters from displaying properly\n- Ensure all filter buttons are fully visible and accessible\n- Improve button arrangement (consider wrapping, scrolling, or responsive grid layout)\n- Verify proper spacing and alignment between filter buttons\n- Test responsive behavior across different screen sizes (mobile, tablet, desktop)\n- Ensure visual consistency with the rest of the gallery interface\n- Confirm all filters remain functional after layout fixes\n\nEdge cases to consider:\n- Long filter label text\n- Large number of filter options\n- Small viewport sizes\n- Dynamic addition or removal of filters",
